name: GOUT Coin
description: Nov 12, 2024: A then-unknown MEME coin launched on BSC and skyrocketed 1,800× in 18 days, igniting a late-2024 FOMO wave. Sept 2025: As OKB strengthened, OKX’s X Layer 1 emerged as a new hub for MEME traders, driven by top traffic and exchange reach. Oct 1, 2025: At the Token2049 week in Singapore, the original GOUT team said they’d restart the “30 days to 10,000×” plan after linking up with X Layer leadership.
